text: Birkenfeld is a community in Main-Spessart in the Regierungsbezirk of Lower Franconia (Unterfranken) in Bavaria, Germany and a member of the Verwaltungsgemeinschaft (Administrative Community) of Marktheidenfeld. ==Geography== ===Location=== Birkenfeld is in the Main Spessart Region. The community has the following Gemarkungen (traditional rural cadastral areas): Billingshausen, Birkenfeld. ==References== Category:Main-Spessart
title: Birkenfeld, Bavaria
